T1  - Effect of Aloe vera (Barbadensis Mill) on Letrozole Induced Polycystic Ovarian Syndrome in Swiss Albino Mice.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.4103/jhrs.jhrs_22_22
A1  - Ghagane, Shridhar C
A1  - Toragall, Makhadumsab M
A1  - Akbar, A Aimen
