T1  - A randomized trial of endometrial scratching in women with PCOS undergoing ovulation induction cycles.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.rbmo.2021.10.008
A1  - Glanville, Elizabeth Joan
A1  - Wilkinson, Jack
A1  - Sadler, Lynn
A1  - Wong, Tze Yoong
A1  - Acharya, Santanu
