T1  - Sexual function in infertile women with polycystic ovary syndrome and unexplained infertility.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.ajog.2017.04.034
A1  - Diamond, Michael P
A1  - Legro, Richard S
A1  - Coutifaris, Christos
