T1  - Impact of Male and Female Weight, Smoking, and Intercourse Frequency on Live Birth in Women With Polycystic Ovary Syndrome.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1210/jc.2015-1178
A1  - Polotsky, Alex J
