N2  - The manuscript deals with the tolerability of Lamotrigine in women. The recent literature is reviewed with respect to interactions with oral contraceptives, sexuality, infertility, interactions with sex hormones, polycystic ovarian syndrome, adipositas, cosmetic side effects, osteoporosis, pregnancy, breast feeding, and teratogenetic effects. The available data have practical implications for the safe use of Lamotrigine in women.
