T1  - Pelvic ultrasonography in girls with precocious puberty, congenital adrenal hyperplasia, obesity, or hirsutism.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/s0022-3476(88)80208-7
A1  - Salardi, S
A1  - Orsini, L F
A1  - Cacciari, E
